{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_07_01_short",
  "title": "川咲さくら (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんから聞いたんですけど、サニーピースに\n遊園地からオファーが来たって本当ですか？",
      "startTime": 4.4333334048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "遊園地でライブするなんて楽しみです\n遊びに来たお客さんを笑顔にしちゃいますよー",
      "startTime": 12.0666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。乗り気になっているところ悪いが\nその仕事は断るつもりなんだ",
      "startTime": 19.4535204284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、どうしてですか？",
      "startTime": 22.353107357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "向こうが指定した日程に、サニピの五人を揃えるのは\nスケジュール的に無理なんだ",
      "startTime": 28.6345585505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "五人とも個人での仕事が増えてきて\n都合がつかなかったんだよ",
      "startTime": 33.4012252171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか……\nみんなで歌いたかったな……",
      "startTime": 38.4666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "先方も残念に思うはずだ。サニピのライブを\n遊園地を立て直すきっかけにしたいと言っていたからな",
      "startTime": 44.6640825907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "立て直す……？\nもしかして、その遊園地は経営が苦しいんですか？",
      "startTime": 50.8000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "詳しくは分からないが\nお客さんの数が年々減っているのは事実らしい",
      "startTime": 57.5913860956,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}